                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2557" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0549</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8261 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">完美品牌升级，化解I Do“幸福的烦恼”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Perfect Brand Upgrade Dissolved the “Happy Worry” of I Do</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">臧岳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国传媒大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潘建新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">I Do公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">定位；品牌升级；品牌传播；品牌资产管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Positioning, Brand Upgrade, Brand Communication, Brand Equity Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了，2006年，李厚霖凭借自身多年行业从业经验，准确地判断了当时国内珠宝行业发展瓶颈，并预测了未来珠宝市场消费趋势。因此，他决心摒弃国内传统珠宝品牌大而全的经营模式，转而将目标投向婚嫁珠宝细分市场，创立国内首个情感珠宝品牌I Do。此后，经过近十年的发展，I Do已稳坐国内婚嫁珠宝市场的头把交椅。2014年前后，随着国内经济的走低，珠宝市场也呈现了萎靡的态势，然而I Do却因为早先准确地抓住婚嫁消费这个刚需市场，在其它品牌经营状况频频亮起红灯时，自身业绩却节节走高。此时，另一个“幸福的烦恼”却开始困扰起I Do，当老客户几年后重返品牌时，却由于I Do多年专注婚嫁市场，产品线较为单一，无法满足这些老客户的二次消费需求。对此，李厚霖意识到倘若要全面满足这些老客户的需求，并非是拓宽产品线那么简单，必须要进行品牌整体升级。然而，对于是否进行品牌升级公司内部有些不同声音，在经过一番调研论证后，公司管理层洞察到未来婚后珠宝市场的巨大潜力。在李厚霖的坚持下，品牌升级工作走上日程。最终，在经过长达两年的筹备和几轮精彩的传播战后，I Do品牌升级正式拉开序幕，开启了品牌新篇章。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">By virtue of his years of experience, Li Houlin, chairman of HIERSUN Group, accurately grasped the development bottleneck of the domestic jewelry industry and future domestic jewelry consumption trend in 2006. Li Houlin determined to abandon traditional domestic jewelry brand and the “large and all-inclusive” business model, turning the target to invest in wedding jewelry market segments, founded the first domestic emotional jewelry brand “I Do”. After nearly a decade of development, I Do has become the top spot in the wedding jewelry market. There are more than 500 shops in over 150 cities at home and abroad. The total number of employees has reached 6000. Loyal customers are up to 500,000. The number of online platform fans are more than one million. Around 2014, with the domestic economic downturn, the jewelry market was also showing a trend of sluggish. However, because of earlier accurately seizing of the rigid demand of the wedding consumption market, I Do performance has been steadily higher while other competitors’ operating conditions frequently raised red flags. But another &quot;happy worry&quot; troubled I Do. The old customers of this brand have bought I Do rings when they got married. However, when they returned to the stores to select gifts at their marriage anniversaries, their secondary demand couldn’t be met. Because of working deeply in the marriage market for many years, I Do lacked related products for the married market. In view of this problem, Li Houlin realized that if they want to fully meet the needs of these old customers, they couldn’t just to broaden the product line, but also had to carry out a comprehensive brand upgrade program. Brand upgrade is far-reaching. Although this work was very difficult and there were different opinions, under Chairman Li Houlin’s insist, brand upgrade work was on its agenda. Ultimately, after more than two years of preparation and a perfect round of spread, I Do brand upgrade had a successful completion.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-11</td>
                            </tr>
